The AWS CloudFormation template for this Serverless application

/Users/admin/Desktop/Portfolio/ecommerce.serviceRawFile:
service: ecommerce-backend  # Ensure the service name is defined

provider:
  name: aws
  runtime: nodejs18.x  # Choose a supported Node.js runtime

functions:
  getProducts:
    handler: handler.getProducts
    events:
      - http:
          path: products
          method: get
          cors: true  # Enable CORS

  getProductById:
    handler: handler.getProductById
    events:
      - http:
          path: products/{id}
          method: get
          cors: true  # Enable CORS
  
  createProduct:
    handler: handler.createProduct
    events:
      - http:
          path: products
          method: post
          cors: true  # Enable CORS
